#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
wg-bot-doctor — audit, diagnose, and (optionally) repair a wg-vpn-bot install.

Read-only by default. Use --fix to apply automatic remediation for the
checks that support it.

Usage:
    sudo wg-bot-doctor                  # full audit, no changes
    sudo wg-bot-doctor --fix            # audit + apply safe fixes
    sudo wg-bot-doctor --section bot    # only bot checks
    sudo wg-bot-doctor --section wg     # only WG checks
    sudo wg-bot-doctor --section sys    # only filesystem/perms checks
    sudo wg-bot-doctor --json           # machine-readable output
    sudo wg-bot-doctor --verbose        # show passing checks too

Sections:
    sys   filesystem ownership, modes, FIFO, tmpfiles, sudoers, systemd units
    bot   service state, crash history, Telegram connectivity, state file health
    wg    kernel<->config consistency, IP allocation, peer/claim mapping
"""
